data.description: Move-in ready and well maintained corner lot home located approximately 30 minutes from Philadelphia! This home was renovated in 2019 and features a large living room area that connects with the kitchen area. The kitchen features a nice countertop that divides the living room and kitchen space. The kitchen leads downstairs to the basement which is fully finished including a laundry area and full bathroom. There is also an attached garage in the basement that can be useful for storage.  The third floor include 3 bedrooms and a full bathroom. This home is perfect for a family looking to move right in, don't wait any longer and schedule your showing today! **PLEASE MAKE SURE TO LOCK DOOR.  The only way of locking the door is to push the door towards you, insert the key and turn until locked.**
